In 2017, XXX Village, Dong'an Town, Gaozhou.

Luo's mentally ill wife is locked in an abandoned warehouse. Luo is in his 70s. In 1998, the traffickers brought several mentally ill women to Changpo Town near his home to sell them. The remaining woman was not wanted, so Luo picked her up and took her home as his wife. In 1999 they had a son and later a daughter. This woman can't speak, can't take care of herself, and refuses to wear clothes. Luo doesn't know what her name is, how old she is, and where she came from. For 20 years he locked her in warehouses with farm implements.